            {% case ReminderCount %}
                {% when "1" %}
                    <strong>RE : 1st Reminder Letter </strong>
                {% when "2" %}
                    <strong>RE : 2nd Reminder Letter </strong>
                {% when "3" %}
                    <strong>RE : 3rd Reminder Letter </strong>
            {% endcase %}
        </p>
        <p>
            Dear Sir & Madam,
        </p>

        <p>
            Firstly, we would like to thank you for your trust & cooperation of {{ Name }} to PT. ASURANSI TOTAL BERSAMA. 
        </p>
        {% case ReminderCount %}
            {% when "1" %}
                <p>
                    Based on our records, we would like to inform you that the premium outstanding balance overdue 60 days as of {{ AsAtDateEn }}, are as follows:
                </p>

                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0;">
                    <strong>Total Premium : IDR {{ TotalPremium }} (details attached) </strong>
                </p>

                <p>
                    We highly appreciate your attention & cooperation to inform the client to resolve the above outstandings immediately before
                    <strong>{{ DeadlineDateEn }}</strong>
                </p>
            {% when "2" %}
