                    <strong>Total Premium : IDR {{ TotalPremium }} (details attached) </strong>
                </p>

                <p>
                    We highly appreciate your attention & cooperation to inform the client to resolve the above outstandings immediately before
                    <strong>{{ DeadlineDateEn }}</strong>
                </p>
            {% when "3" %}
