                    {{ AsAtDateEn }}, we would like to remind you that we have not yet received the remittance for the outstanding balance, as follows:
                </p>

                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 0;">
                    <strong>Total Premium : IDR {{ TotalPremium }} (details attached) </strong>
                </p>

